Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.83,0:00:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭禽獸君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.07,0:00:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更討厭禽獸君和姐姐在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.21,0:00:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法選擇糰子會是什麼心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.27,0:00:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醬油糰子？豆餡糰子？芝麻糰子？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.42,0:00:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐總是笑著問我要各種糰子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.66,0:00:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.68,0:00:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我想差不多該說說禽獸君的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.58,0:00:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.09,0:00:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩哥哥早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.30,0:00:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.07,0:00:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 我做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.61,0:00:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禽獸君的報告書
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.23,0:02:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}伊莉絲的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禽獸君來到城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像大吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨我的宮殿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.78,0:02:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來城堡之前 他還不知道席恩哥哥當了國王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禽獸君什麼的 一直關在監獄裡就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想給禽獸君最後一次機會嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 禽獸君是做了十惡不赦的大壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.11,0:02:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才被關進監獄的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納他也有很多內情的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禽獸君是給席恩哥哥寫了很多檢討 你才原諒他的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 某種意義上是對這個世界寫了檢討
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對世界的檢討？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這樣下去世界可能會向不好的方向發展
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓這種事情發生 大家要團結努力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是這意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禽獸君寫的檢討 大家都要反省嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家搞不懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 萊納交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不要隨便決定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了走吧 搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是你搭檔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 姐姐和禽獸君離開了羅蘭德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為席恩哥哥命令他們去找勇者遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是命令啦 是請求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禽獸君找到了勇者遺物 就隨便把它變大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全啥也看不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者覺得煩了就扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從地面上長出了多餘的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.15,0:04:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情總不會一帆風順的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你之前有戴著那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺跡裡撿的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還搶走姐姐好不容易發現的寶石變成魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把周圍一塊統統破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此消滅了4座山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:05:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪禽獸君 各位測量技師不得不重新製作地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地圖雖然能重做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山卻沒那麼簡單就能重造呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還比人先逃一步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混賬 搞毛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此說一下禽獸君的注意事項
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為非常重要 得說兩遍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩哥哥 你要跟著重複哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和禽獸君說話就會懷孕哦 起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和禽獸君說話 就會懷孕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了尋找勇者遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還去鄰國圖書館查了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禽獸君在那裡犯了老毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企圖盜取幼女手中重要的書本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但姐姐不會原諒這種惡行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制裁了禽獸君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 還有這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好險啊 女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.28,0:06:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人是拐騙幼女的慣犯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是尋找勇者遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差旅費也入不敷出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也要做席恩哥哥的護衛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不讓他幹些正經活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預算也批不下來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有情報說席恩哥哥出差的時候被殺手盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禽獸君只發牢騷不幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉好累
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說我們幹嘛非要為席恩做這種麻煩事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是姐姐說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說不給他當保鏢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要拆了維尼特糰子店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐還關注地域附著型產業發展
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以宏觀的視野守護著羅蘭德的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過傷腦筋的是她那產業限定性太大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩哥哥為了避免禽獸君在別國給姐姐添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還送去了優秀的精銳部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是殺害過去同胞的骯髒任務
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後 也有可能因此被人歧視
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝您的關心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:08:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我不在乎受傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經一度放棄生存
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.74,0:08:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避痛苦的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋求解脫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 一個我青梅竹馬的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給了我生存的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想向他報恩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將引以為榮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,執行追擊破忌者的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在奈爾法的遺跡裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禽獸君也是橫行霸道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把收好的槍隨便放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了吸引姐姐的注意還主動跳進火裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這引人注意的方式真夠拚命的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.74,0:08:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著慢著慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐第一時間感知到危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.07,0:09:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知了禽獸君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是禽獸君卻不聽勸告
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還對姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子 這筆賬之後一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂發脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉絲你這混賬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好漲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.82,0:09:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來請聽題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精銳部隊的正式名稱是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破耳朵隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潑沙子隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差得有點遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想偷懶隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉好累
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快解決這遺跡 去吃糰子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是受那花瓶暴力女脅迫的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還可以從輕發落
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這女人是中了你的毒手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,始亂終棄的可憐受害者之一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說誰始亂終棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒有被拋棄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說是一夜情了 好成人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精銳部隊的隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.97,0:10:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和禽獸君有過一夜情 被始亂終棄的舊情人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣禽獸君應該不會對姐姐下手了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納的守備範圍還是那麼寬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.33,0:10:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稀奇的是禽獸君竟然寫信來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:11:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 他竟然報告說找不到勇者遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為別國男女二人組的阻撓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一派胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真是假 的確無人能證實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 財寶就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方好像很強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備隨時逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個財寶都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你把財寶藏哪兒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就沒有這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是來看傳說中的龍了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是丈二和尚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 屍體都沒有流血
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉絲？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事 請你們解釋一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也在找勇者遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就展示一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們所丟棄的遺物的使用方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求雷鳴 電光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.94,0:12:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是勇者遺物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.39,0:12:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 庫的「艾爾克羅諾之鐮」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「朵爾艾利之劍鱗」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及這「愛蕾米奧之簪」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:12:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三件遺物…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去沒勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共鳴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 萊納 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望一切都消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們對萊納做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不使其覺醒 就無法奪取複寫眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺醒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,複寫眼被人厭惡忌諱的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為會失控破壞一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以人稱瘋狂的惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不祥的殺戮者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:14:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉絲…快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離我…遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的…我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會變成怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人會死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這一切都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 結束這一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨心所欲地釋放一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開放 殺戮 所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認持有者崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將大肆破壞而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你也看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那點力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將在這「愛蕾米奧之簪」的神力下化為烏有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解析存在 解除
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧 螻蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.41,0:15:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是普通的複寫眼持有者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要殺吾？用那點力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區愛蕾米奧就想殺了吾？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匍匐在地的螻蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.63,0:16:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧 消失吧消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切皆為無
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.47,0:16:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回歸於無吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.09,0:16:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認為你是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的搭檔 僕從 喝茶的伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.27,0:16:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.54,0:16:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽見嗎 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.22,0:16:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問你聽見了嗎萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.62,0:16:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.83,0:16:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的戲份 已經完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.56,0:17:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 菲莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的眼睛…閉上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊…納
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你不是…怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道禽獸君發什麼瘋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.14,0:17:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企圖拐騙幼童
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐當然反對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但誰也阻止不了失控的禽獸君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禽獸君煽動兒童
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其訓練成戰鬥兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事無可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐極力反對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你改變了魔法的構造吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可 可可
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐從禽獸君手中救下了孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其交給了優秀的精英部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.59,0:18:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐對任何人都很溫柔嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求雷鳴 電光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您冷靜一點 蜜爾可隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.96,0:18:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.93,0:18:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維尼特糰子店剛做好的丸子真是不同凡響啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:18:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從哪兒弄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.67,0:18:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是買來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡是羅蘭德國內啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位於羅蘭德沿岸部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.84,0:19:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我艾利斯家領地之一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.06,0:19:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去找讓我們落到這步田地的席恩報仇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 打倒他的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就自立為王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將羅蘭德變成糰子帝國吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點成果也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禽獸君就這樣回羅蘭德了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是恬不知恥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐總是被禽獸君所玩弄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的報告書十分簡明易懂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 隔壁的禽獸君完成了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…啥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.78,0:19:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞啥啊這
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次旅行就吃了這麼多糰子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.12,0:20:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃多少才夠啊那大胃女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是什麼都能吸收的人體愛蕾米奧之簪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准說姐姐的壞話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞啥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.71,0:20:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝 呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.55,0:20:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？這次出差花了好多伙食費啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報銷差旅費的時候要扣掉椅子的修理費啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…啊？為啥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.06,0:20:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃糰子的是菲莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.61,0:20:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞壞椅子的是那位…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這修理費也要扣掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.15,0:20:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我才不付…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:21:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩哥哥 我很強吧 很強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有你在你姐姐的安全就有保障了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話也要告訴姐姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.65,0:21:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說伊莉絲是很能幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.59,0:21:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那禽獸男一起旅行讓我有所顧慮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃的糰子竟然不夠平時的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪覺得身子不夠靈活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能這樣下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說晚上攝取糰子會破壞女性的曲線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.55,0:21:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這也是為了和變態王國國王繼續旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.91,0:21:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久違的維尼特糰子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.23,0:21:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美味了

Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.91,0:23:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.13,0:23:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我在羅蘭德一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.51,0:23:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會被那十惡不赦目中無人的傢伙使喚到死

Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不趕快離開這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.88,0:23:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我預感到事情會變得越來越麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.07,0:23:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}不會微笑的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.83,0:23:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好菲莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.91,0:23:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快準備出發
